34Dwarf_Unsigned
35dwarf_add_die_to_debug(Dwarf_P_Debug dbg, Dwarf_P_Die first_die,
36 Dwarf_Error *error)
37{
38
39 if (dbg == NULL || first_die == NULL) {
40 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
41 return (DW_DLV_NOCOUNT);
42 }
43
44 dbg->dbgp_root_die = first_die;
45
46 return (DW_DLV_OK);
47}
48
49Dwarf_P_Die
50dwarf_new_die(Dwarf_P_Debug dbg, Dwarf_Tag new_tag,
51 Dwarf_P_Die parent, Dwarf_P_Die child, Dwarf_P_Die left_sibling,
52 Dwarf_P_Die right_sibling, Dwarf_Error *error)
53{
54 Dwarf_P_Die die;
55 int count;
56
57 if (dbg == NULL) {
58 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
59 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
60 }
61
62 count = _dwarf_die_count_links(parent, child, left_sibling,
63 right_sibling);
64
65 if (count > 1) {
66 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
67 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
68 }
69
70 if (_dwarf_die_alloc(dbg, &die, error) != DW_DLE_NONE)
71 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
72
73 die->die_dbg = dbg;
74 die->die_tag = new_tag;
75
76 STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL(&dbg->dbgp_dielist, die, die_pro_next);
77
78 if (count == 0)
79 return (die);
80
81 _dwarf_die_link(die, parent, child, left_sibling, right_sibling);
82
83 return (die);
84}
85
86Dwarf_P_Die
87dwarf_die_link(Dwarf_P_Die die, Dwarf_P_Die parent,
88 Dwarf_P_Die child, Dwarf_P_Die left_sibling, Dwarf_P_Die right_sibling,
89 Dwarf_Error *error)
90{
91 Dwarf_Debug dbg;
92 int count;
93
94
95 if (die == NULL) {
96 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
97 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
98 }
99
100 dbg = die->die_dbg;
101 count = _dwarf_die_count_links(parent, child, left_sibling,
102 right_sibling);
103
104 if (count > 1) {
105 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
106 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
107 } else if (count == 0)
108 return (die);
109
110 _dwarf_die_link(die, parent, child, left_sibling, right_sibling);
111
112 return (die);
113}
